description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Bank position within Endoscopy at Sandwell and West Birmingham NHS Trust. This specialty requires a proactive individual capable of taking responsibility for ensuring achievement of national waiting time targets and managing efficient booking processes across multiple sites in response to the needs of a diverse and critical patient group. Experience and knowledge in endoscopy bookings is essential including waiting list experience and knowledge of endoscopy procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder must have excellent communication and organisational skills, the ability to prioritise their own workload and have a professional attitude. They must be capable of liaising professionally with patients, and with colleagues at all levels, including senior consultants and nurses from across the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will also need an overview of the national 6 week diagnostic target, cancer pathways and 18 week pathway management systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Nikole Hazeldine-Potts Job title Service Manager Email address nikole.hazeldine-potts@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
